msgstr "5-7 英寸碎木机"

#. module: agri_equipment_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agri_equipment_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "想与我们讨论您的 Odoo 设置或更进一步吗？"

#. module: agri_equipment_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agri_equipment_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr "您可以在主仪表板上访问 Odoo 数据库中每个已安装的应用程序。"

#. module: agri_equipment_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agri_equipment_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"您已完成该演示使用案例！除此之外，还有千百种其他方法去调整 Odoo 设定，以满足"
"您业务的特别需求。"

#. module: agri_equipment_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agri_equipment_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Agri-Equipment Rental package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"您尚未导入演示数据？现在仍可进行。请前往应用&gt; 行业 &gt; 升级您的农业设备租"
"赁套件，并勾选相关选项"

#. module: agri_equipment_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agri_equipment_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for <strong>Agri-Equipment Rental "
"</strong>package. By doing so, we have installed a bunch of necessary apps "
"to run your business efficiently."
msgstr ""
"您刚刚安装了 Odoo 针对<strong>的农业设备出租</strong>套件。通过此次安装，我们"
"已为您安装了一系列必要应用，以帮助您高效运营业务。"

#. module: agri_equipment_rental
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agri_equipment_rental.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might have tested this package with or without demo data.<br/>In any "
"case, you may have written records in journals which are not deletable and "
"which might be an issue for your traceability."
msgstr ""
"您可能在安装时选择加载或不加载演示数据。<br/>\n"
"无论哪种情况，系统中可能已存在不可删除的日记账记录，这可能会影响您的数据追溯"
"。"

#. module: agri_equipment_rental
